      • triggerMasterHooks

        public static java.util.List<MasterState> triggerMasterHooks(java.util.Collection<MasterTriggerRestoreHook<?>> hooks,
                                                             long checkpointId,
                                                             long timestamp,
                                                             java.util.concurrent.Executor executor,
                                                             Time timeout)
                                                      throws FlinkException
        Triggers all given master hooks and returns state objects for each hook that produced a state.
        参数:
        hooks - The hooks to trigger
        checkpointId - The checkpoint ID of the triggering checkpoint
        timestamp - The (informational) timestamp for the triggering checkpoint
        executor - An executor that can be used for asynchronous I/O calls
        timeout - The maximum time that a hook may take to complete
        返回:
        A list containing all states produced by the hooks
        抛出:
        FlinkException - Thrown, if the hooks throw an exception, or the state+ deserialization fails.

      • restoreMasterHooks

        public static void restoreMasterHooks(java.util.Map<java.lang.String,MasterTriggerRestoreHook<?>> masterHooks,
                                      java.util.Collection<MasterState> states,
                                      long checkpointId,
                                      boolean allowUnmatchedState,
                                      org.slf4j.Logger log)
                               throws FlinkException
        Calls the restore method given checkpoint master hooks and passes the given master state to them where state with a matching name is found.

        If state is found and no hook with the same name is found, the method throws an exception, unless the allowUnmatchedState flag is set.

        参数:
        masterHooks - The hooks to call restore on
        states - The state to pass to the hooks
        checkpointId - The checkpoint ID of the restored checkpoint
        allowUnmatchedState - True,
        log - The logger for log messages
        抛出:
        FlinkException - Thrown, if the hooks throw an exception, or the state+ deserialization fails.
